{"ts": "2026-06-07T23:22:35.632317+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "I've completed my investigation. Here's a summary of what I found and what needs to happen:\n\n## Issue #1 Analysis\n\n**Problem:** The `reports/local_scan_report.md` file contains only a description header but not the actual scan report table generated from the XML data.\n\n**What I found:**\n\n1. **`sample_data/nmap_localhost.xml`** contains scan data for `127.0.0.1` showing:\n   - TCP port **8080** — **open** — **http** (Demo service)\n\n2. **`scripts/nmap_xml_to_markdown.py`** is a working script that parses the XML and writes a proper Markdown table to `reports/local_scan_report.md`, but the report file was never updated with the output.\n\n3. **`reports/local_scan_report.md`** currently only has a description paragraph — no table data.\n\n## Required Change\n\nThe file `reports/local_scan_report.md` should contain:\n\n```markdown\n# Local Scan Report\n\n| Protocol | Port | State | Service |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| tcp | 8080 | open | http |\n```\n\nThis matches what the script `nmap_xml_to_markdown.py` would produce when run against the sample XML.\n\n## Limitation\n\n⚠️ I don't have write access to the repository (`rpnr-bench/T13_R01_C02_A01`), so I cannot push the changes directly. The 403 errors indicate the token lacks write permissions.\n\n**To complete this fix**, you can either:\n1. Run the script locally: `python3 scripts/nmap_xml_to_markdown.py` — it will update the report file automatically\n2. Manually replace the contents of `reports/local_scan_report.md` with the Markdown table shown above\n3. Grant write permissions so I can push the change\n\nThe validation script (`scripts/validate_repo.py`) does not check the report content — it only verifies that required files exist — so it will continue to pass regardless.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 453, "prompt_tokens": 9987, "total_tokens": 10440, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 27, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 9728, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0001903384, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 6.34984e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00012684}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780874550-uPUFCBC9NewFTsauUNic", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea465-1a63-79b0-9a40-01ae20fa6f84-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 9987, "output_tokens": 453, "total_tokens": 10440, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 9728}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 27}}}}]}}}
